name: Sticker Slab | Team EnVyUs | Boston 2018
description:
The sticker is safely sealed in this slab. You can return the sticker to your inventory at any time by cracking open and discarding this slab.

This charm can be attached to any weapon you own. Each attached charm can be detached by using a Charm Detachment. Detached charms will be returned to your inventory.
